{
  "stem": "802.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was allowed at the time-- certainly at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, in fact, a friend of mine told me that she was in that-- in-- in one of those groups.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't want to mention her name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She's very famous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she told me about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was shocked that a Jewish woman would do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she took pride, but she was also a little bit reluctant to tell me this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you had these ambivalent feelings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now-- but at the same time, it's not because we're cowardly, but it was part of our culture.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, but at the same time, the-- the kids who were able to get to go to Palestine, the Jews who were able to finally get to Palestine with enormous difficulties, as you probably know, they were the ones who fought the 1948 War.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my very dear friend was killed during that war, who also survived Plaszow, among other things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were-- it was not cowardice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] it was a matter of ethics-- ethical values, you know, and-- and moral values, which is-- Jews don't kill, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, take us to 1947 in the States when you were here with your mother and your sister, and a little worried about being a single woman.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We never separated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed with my uncle for about a week in-- in Brooklyn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we moved to my aunt in the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while we were still with my uncle, I guess we were with them more than a week.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It must have been maybe two weeks, because I got my first job, sewing buttons on Grand Street, in Manhattan, you know, lower Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my boss-- I learned to sew quite well during the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
